item.title: Hands on Session On Developing A Zip Archive using Python
item.description:
Not only attendees will learn to code a Python program that could create zip-archives from the ground-up, but they will also get a chance to win lot of goodies and stickers.

We also thank our community partners, GitHub Campus Experts.

Please fill in this form to register for the event. The seats are filling fast (we already have 150+ registrations till date), so hurry up!!!

You'll receive an email with link to join the session which will be held on August 30, 2021 at 12:00 PM IST on YouTube.
